{"type": "article", "id": 7471, "title": "据说 2015 流行这 9 种搭配，我们觉得都没啥用", "description": "而且完全没有新意可言。", "date": "2015-03-17T13:54:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7849, "name": "2015秋冬"}, {"id": 7850, "name": "流行配饰"}], "category": 19, "column": null, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605202228MvJC59dK7hZAfLsE.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/seasons/fall-2015\" target=\"_blank\"> <span>2015 </span>年秋季的秀</a>基本都已经走完了。每一个时尚季，配饰都是服装之外极富乐趣的部分，<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/03/fall-2015-accessories\" target=\"_blank\">Fashionista 网站</a>最近就总结了几个配饰上的新趋势，看看这些大耳环、长系带靴，是不是都挺眼熟？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>贝雷帽</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052022243f1y92UCqGTPoNmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右：</em><span><em>Fay, Paul &amp; Joe, Gucci, Luisa Beccaria </em></span><em>和</em><span><em> Gucci. 图片来源: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>Gucci </span>和<span> MXMJ 重新</span>将贝雷帽带回了 <span>T </span>台。不论是松软的造型还是挺硬的廓形，都给整套服装增添了成熟的意味。但是你知道的，这可能是日常生活里最难驾驭的配饰，戴得好文艺青年，戴得不好……就和所有最差装扮效果一样。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>毛毛鞋</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202224Dfs2pqRbkMvhV9xL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Fendi, Gucci, Maison Margiela, Antonio Marras </em></span><em>和</em><span><em> Tibi. </em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><em><em style=\"white-space:normal;\">图片来源</em>: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t呵呵。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>丝绒面料的高跟鞋</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202225aQXhxwAoJz43iSbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Givenchy, Dolce &amp; Gabbana, Emilio Pucci </em></span><em>和 </em><span><em>Stella\r\nMcCartney. <em style=\"white-space:normal;\">图片来源</em>: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t美！千万不要穿着它走大马路！这种鞋穿上就是为了被脱下来！\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>大号胸针</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202225rbVzwHI9SZk2sic5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Fausto Puglisi, Edun, Balenciaga, Prada </em></span><em>和</em><span><em> Luisa\r\nBeccaria.  <em style=\"white-space:normal;\">图片来源</em>: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>皮毛围巾</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202226sQiqvghX0RGupL3y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Tod's, Michael Kors, Donna Karan, Dries van Noten </em></span><em>和 </em><span><em>Givenchy. <em style=\"white-space:normal;\">图片来源</em>: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t环保主义者会再次为它热血沸腾的。除了 T 台和时装周街拍，能用好皮草的场合真是少之又少，不算是一个有性价比的投资对象。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>大号包包</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202226vueVK6CSAQ4iIhRt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Sally Lapointe, Moschino, Philipp Plein and Roksanda. Photos:\r\nImaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t如果把双肩包也算在大号包包里，多少觉得时尚界有点随意。大包的精髓可能在于“不要装满”，尤其是“不要用有份量的东西（例如文件）装满”，否则你必须承担得起挎着它雷厉风行穿越人群的成本。优雅也是需要体力的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>系带长靴</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202227MAxvg5ojpBbfqLE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Giambattista Valli, Rodarte, Altuzarra, Francesco Scognamiglio </em></span><em>和 </em><span><em>Vionnet.\r\nPhotos: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t《50 度灰》过于流行了吧？\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong>单只耳环</strong><span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202227jb2xiIeyzCSdkPuc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Anteprima, Isabel Marant, Balmain, Christian Dior </em></span><em>和</em><span><em> Tibi.\r\nPhotos: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t其实单只耳环已经在 <span>T </span>台上待了好几个赛季了。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong>Matchy-matchy</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span><strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605202228B5Oa8ltmHqwSi6PE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<em>从左到右</em><span><em>: Tod's, Boss, Victoria Beckham 和 The Row. Photos: Imaxtree</em></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t今年秋季，与衣服同一颜色、同一材质的包包流行了起来，包成为了服饰的延伸。估计很少有人有财力能做得到日日 match，最好卖的恐怕也还是百搭款吧。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://fashionista.com/2015/03/fall-2015-accessories\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;outline:#000000;white-space:normal;\">Fashionista</a> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}